<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/351486-what-did-the-wolf-symbolize">What did the wolf symbolize?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_351486'><a id="like_count_community_question_351486" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/351486?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">17 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F12875258-tell-the-wolves-i-m-home">like</a></span>

