<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/635968-give-me-some-feedback---is-this-an">Give me some feedback - is this an engaging book for a group of 40-50 yr old women to read for our intellectual book club?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_635968'><a id="like_count_community_question_635968" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/635968?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">7 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F12875258-tell-the-wolves-i-m-home">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/635968-give-me-some-feedback---is-this-an">5 years ago</a>
</li>
